      "name": "Yield force QoI comparison — FEA vs. experimental (N=11)",
      "description": "FEA-predicted yield force of 1247 N compared against experimental mean of 1219 N (SD 61 N). Relative difference 2.3%, E/uval 0.74. Acceptance criterion satisfied.",
      "comparedAgainst": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/data/lab-a-compression-bending-n6",
      "prov:wasGeneratedBy": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/activity/val-run-yield-force-2023-11-22"
    },
