      "description": "FEA-predicted force at 40 mm displacement of 2104 N compared against experimental mean of 2078 N (SD 94 N). Relative difference 1.25%, E/uval 0.44. Acceptance criterion satisfied.",
      "comparedAgainst": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/data/lab-b-compression-bending-n5",
      "prov:wasGeneratedBy": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/activity/val-run-force40mm-2023-11-22"
