      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "All three FEA codes (Ansys 2023 R1, FDA in-house solver, DePuy Synthes proprietary code) are subject to formal SQA programs. Ansys holds ISO 9001 certification; FDA in-house solver is governed by 21 CFR Part 820 software controls; DePuy Synthes code is validated under IEC 62304. Version control, regression test suites, and release notes are documented for each code. Achieved level 3 exceeds required level 2 for Medium model risk."
    },
    {
