      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "FEA boundary conditions replicate ASTM F1717 fixture geometry to within 0.1 mm. Load application point, fixture span (100 mm), and constraint conditions are directly mapped from the test setup drawings. Cross-verification between three independent FEA implementations confirms consistent input parameterisation."
    },
    {
