      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Relative difference < 10% on all QoIs; E/uval < 1.96 on all QoIs.",
      "rationale": "Three QoIs compared: stiffness (2.95% difference, E/uval 0.81), yield force (2.3% difference, E/uval 0.74), force at 40 mm (1.25% difference, E/uval 0.44). All acceptance criteria satisfied. Validation uncertainty uval computed per ASME V&V 20 incorporating experimental measurement uncertainty and numerical uncertainty."
    },
    {
